    <ul>
        <li><strong>Real-time Updates:</strong> Stay up-to-date with the latest news regarding the college bus system, ensuring users are well-informed about any changes or developments.</li>
        <li><strong>Announcements:</strong> Important announcements related to bus schedules, system maintenance, and other pertinent information are prominently displayed for easy visibility.</li>
